title: ‘What about Hillary’s lies and corruption?’: Jane Fonda called out over anti-Trump tweet
text:
‘What about Hillary’s lies and corruption?’: Jane Fonda called out over anti-Trump tweet Posted at 7:26 pm on January 10, 2017 by William A. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Actress and activist Jane Fonda took to Twitter Tuesday night to attack Donald Trump. When Trump’s racist homophobic misogynistic anti-environment administration comes for any of us it comes for us all https://t.co/IaFqdsKMTC 
— Jane Seymour Fonda (@Janefonda) January 10, 2017 
Some on Twitter took exception to her tweet: @Janefonda What about Hillarys lies and corruption?? no comments?? 
— Merle Terlesky (@MerleTerlesky) January 10, 2017 @Janefonda please stop. We need to heal as a country. I may not of been a supporter but I am exhausted from all the hate from the left
